    • getReferencedModePart

      default ModelPart getReferencedModePart()
      Whereas getReferencedMappingContainer() and getReferencedMappingType() return the referenced container type, this method returns the referenced part. E.g. for a many-to-one this method returns the ToOneAttributeMapping while getReferencedMappingContainer() and getReferencedMappingType() return the referenced EntityMappingType.
